=flash_info
您的邮箱 <span class='loud'>#{@invitation.contact_email}</span>（用于登录，您在 mindpin 的唯一标示）

- mindpin_form_for User.new,:url=>"/invitations/#{@invitation.code}/regeist" do |f|
  = f.hidden_field :email,:value=>@invitation.contact_email
  = f.text_field :name,:maxlength=>50,:desc=>'显示的名称，必填，以后可以修改'
  = f.password_field :password,:value=>'',:maxlength=>32
  = f.password_field :password_confirmation,:value=>'',:maxlength=>32
  .form_actions
    = f.submit "确认注册"